艾里在2012年的喜剧《男人行不行》和其2014年的续集《男人行不行2》中饰演多利安<ref>{{cite news|author=Kristen Page-Kirby|title=Michael Ealy says 'Think Like a Man Too' ups the romantic ante|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/express/wp/2014/06/20/michael-ealy-says-think-like-a-man-too-ups-the-romantic-ante/|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2014-06-20|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2017-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226132315/https://www.washingtonpost.com/express/wp/2014/06/20/michael-ealy-says-think-like-a-man-too-ups-the-romantic-ante/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在2012年励志电影《無條件》中饰演「乔爸爸」<ref>{{cite news|title=Michael Ealy talks unconditional|url=http://www.blackenterprise.com/lifestyle/michael-ealy-unconditional-movie-interview/|website=blackenterprise.com|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2017-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027144529/http://www.blackenterprise.com/lifestyle/michael-ealy-unconditional-movie-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在《男人行不行》和2014年的《昨夜風流》都与[[凱文·哈特|凱文·哈特]]饰演对手戏<ref>{{cite news|author=|title=Michael Ealy: 'I Had To Lose 25 Pounds For 'About Last Night' Role'|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/02/09/michael-ealy-i-had-lose-25-pounds-about-last-night-role_n_4756101.html|work=The Grio|via=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|date=2014-02-09|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2017-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319000017/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/02/09/michael-ealy-i-had-lose-25-pounds-about-last-night-role_n_4756101.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年，艾里与[[福克斯廣播公司|福克斯廣播公司]]签约，在电视剧《[[機器之心|機器之心]]》中饰演「多利安」。这一部科幻警方侦察片设定在2048年，其描述了两个警察使用一些复杂的科技来解决未来犯罪，因而产生了情愫。艾里饰演机器人「多利安」，这一个老一点的机器模型因为有人工情绪而经常被认为不太可靠，而他的任务是去保护其拍档约翰·肯尼士（[[卡爾·厄本|卡爾·厄本]]饰演）<ref>{{cite journal|author=Natalie Abrams|title=Almost Human's Michael Ealy Dissects Dorian|url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/almost-human-michael-ealy-1073835.aspx|work=[[電視指南_(美國雜誌)|TV Guide]]|date=2013-11-24|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103050205/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Almost-Human-Michael-Ealy-1073835.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这部电视剧于2013年至2014年在福克斯播映了一季<ref>{{cite news|author=Nellie Andreeva|title=Fox Drama 'Almost Human' Cancelled|url=http://deadline.com/2014/04/fox-drama-almost-human-cancelled-721643/|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2014-04-29|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201065053/https://deadline.com/2014/04/fox-drama-almost-human-cancelled-721643/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，他在电视剧《[[殺手信徒|殺手信徒]]》第三季饰演连环杀手「特奥」<ref>{{cite news|title=Michael Ealy's Big Bad on 'The Following' Is No Clown|url=https://www.yahoo.com/tv/michael-ealys-big-bad-on-the-following-is-no-115034238905.html|work=Yahoo!|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-09-28|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305133355/https://www.yahoo.com/tv/michael-ealys-big-bad-on-the-following-is-no-115034238905.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾里参演了美國廣播公司的犯罪悬疑电视剧《[[祕密與謊言_(電視劇)|祕密與謊言]]》第二季，而其于2016年停止播映<ref>{{cite journal|author=Shelli Weinstein|title=Michael Ealy Joins Secrets & Lies For the Next Tragic Murder Mystery|url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/michael-ealy-joins-secrets-and-lies-season-2/|work=[[電視指南_(美國雜誌)|TV Guide]]|date=2015-06-17|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118052719/https://www.tvguide.com/news/michael-ealy-joins-secrets-and-lies-season-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他目前在《[[玛丽简的单身生活|玛丽简的单身生活]]》第四季主演<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bet.com/shows/being-mary-jane/news/michael-ealy-joins-being-mary-jane.html|title=Ladies Your #MCM Is Coming to Being Mary Jane!|newspaper=BET.com|access-date=2017-01-17|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124155002/https://www.bet.com/shows/being-mary-jane/news/michael-ealy-joins-being-mary-jane.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==私人生活==
2012年10月，艾里与其交往4年的女朋友卡蒂拉·拉菲格扎達（{{lang|en|Khatira Rafiqzada}}<!--波斯語q譯音“格”，同信息框注釋-->）结婚，并在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]举行婚礼<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20658215,00.html|title=Michael Ealy Quietly Married Longtime Girlfriend in October|date=2012-12-20|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|accessdate=2012-12-27|journal=|archive-date=2016-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527064511/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20658215,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，共育有一子一女<ref>{{cite journal|title=Michael Ealy Announces He Has a Son|url=http://www.essence.com/2014/02/15/michael-ealy-son-khatira-rafiqzada/|work=Essence|date=2014-02-15|accessdate=2014-09-05|journal=|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227122010/https://www.essence.com/2014/02/15/michael-ealy-son-khatira-rafiqzada|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://madamenoire.com/440122/michael-ealy-finally-opened-marriage|title=Michael Ealy Finally Opens Up About His Marriage And Son|author=Jazmine Denise Rogers|date=2014-06-18|work=MadameNoire|access-date=2017-02-25|archive-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621193701/https://madamenoire.com/440122/michael-ealy-finally-opened-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/808486/surprise-michael-ealy-welcomes-a-baby-girl-with-wife-khatira-rafiqzada|title=Surprise! Michael Ealy Welcomes Baby Girl With Wife Khatira Rafiqzada|newspaper=E! Online|access-date=2017-01-17|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211172445/http://www.eonline.com/news/808486/surprise-michael-ealy-welcomes-a-baby-girl-with-wife-khatira-rafiqzada|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

